291
00:15:25,287 --> 00:15:27,558
♪Imperishable♪

292
00:15:29,696 --> 00:15:32,737
♪Bloodstained vows
with a touch of tenderness♪

293
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:39,169
♪Fate is written by the universe♪

294
00:15:40,117 --> 00:15:43,227
♪Unending♪

295
00:15:44,449 --> 00:15:45,281
